assword any time that you visit the portal home page select the “change password” link under the my account heading enter your current password enter your new password confirm your new password and press the “submit” button password expiration boeing security policy requires that passwords be changed every  days you can change it sooner if you like a notice will automatically remind you after  days passwords may not be reused therefore you always need to enter a new one after the expiration date password reset if you forget or lose your password please use the selfservice password reset tool located on the portal logon screen press the blue button titled forgot your password you may also call the boeing enterprise help desk these password reset tool will only work if you have selected your challengeresponse pairs for verification authorized public key infrastructure pki or x certificate users if your organization has a pki agreement with boeing your pki certificate may be used to log in the first time you use a pki certificate you will be prompted to login using your userid and password so that your pki certificate can be associated to your userid if your organization does not have a pki agreement with boeing your browser will report an error if you receive an error use your userid and password to log in to get an account contact your boeing representative or the boeing focal who controls the information that you desire access to obtain additional help for accounts and password resets at the boeing enterprise help desk customers partners suppliers   boeing employees usa and international callers dial   boeing employees usa only toll free   note international callers  usa country code is  return to the secure access welcome page boeing defense overview boeing share defense broad expertise integrated systems boeing’s expertise spans a broad range of products in defense fighter jets rotorcraft embedded product support cybersecurity products surveillance suites advanced